                        <p><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Bigyan Bhawan, G.S. Road, Guwahati-781005</p>
                        <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> 069138 48401</p>
                        <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> dirassac2021@gmail.com</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            
        </div>
        <div class="footer-bottom">
              <p>&copy; 2024 Assam–Nagaland Border Monitoring System. All rights reserved.</p>
